<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">Apache-MySQL-PHP Installation</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">#: Written by KFH:</span><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);"> karshi.hasanov@utoronto.ca</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">#: Date: Sep. 20, 2012</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">#: Description: Things needed for developing a web software</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">#: Last Modified: April 2, 2018</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Apache 2.4 Server</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To see the Apache version on your Mac OS X:</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt;<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 38, 0);"> </span></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 38, 0);">sudo</span> <span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/usr/sbin/httpd -V</span></span></font></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica;"># To check if the Apacher Server is running:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-family: Helvetica;">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> apachect</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica;">l   </span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica;"># If it returns nothing means it is NOT running</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica;"># To start the Server:</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">apachectl</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> <span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(0, 145, 147);">start</span></span></font></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To check the HTTPD main config file syntax:</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt;<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-weight: normal;"> sudo </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-weight: bold;">apachectl</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> <span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(4, 51, 255);">configtest</span></span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">The main configuration file is </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"> “</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/etc/apache2</span>/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">httpd.conf</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">”</span></div><div>The Apache Server will run under:</div><div><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">User</span> </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 143, 0);">_www</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-weight: bold;">Group</span> <span style="color: rgb(0, 145, 147);">_www</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-weight: bold;">ServerAdmin</span><span style="color: rgb(79, 143, 0); font-weight: bold;"> karshi.hasanov@utoronto.ca</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-weight: bold;">ServerName</span><span style="color: rgb(79, 143, 0); font-weight: bold;"> imac.karshi.ca</span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">Note: Do NOT chnage the User and Group since they defined by the system</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146);">          unless you know how to create a user and group under MAC OS!</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">The System Wide HTTP Configuration Files</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># The documents are located in</span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica Neue" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">/Library/WebServer/Documents/</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div># The Web Address for the default root:</div><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 150, 255);">http://localhost  </span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 150, 255);">http://127.0.0.1</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">User Specific HTTP Config Files are located in:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica;">/etc/apache2/users</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">The </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> physical location of a User Web files</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: italic; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">/Users/khasanov/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: italic; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Sites</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: italic; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">  </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;"> ( or </span><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">~/Sites )</span></span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 47, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">IMPORTANT:</span><span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> The folder “Sites” does not exist by default!</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica;">1.</span><span style="color: rgb(146, 144, 0); font-family: Helvetica;"> Create the folder</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">     =&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mkdir</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;"> /Users/khasanov/Sites</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">2. </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(146, 144, 0); font-family: Helvetica;">Create the Config file for a User in</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica;">/etc/apache2/users:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">     </span>=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> vim</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"> /etc/apache2/users/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">khasanov.conf</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"> and add the content:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">    </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(148, 55, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">&lt;Directory</span><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> "</span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/Users/khasanov/Sites/</span><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">"&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">        </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">AllowOverride</span><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(79, 143, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">All</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">       </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Options</span><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> Indexes MultiViews FollowSymLinks</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">        </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Require</span><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(79, 143, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">all granted</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">    <span style="font-size: 17px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 55, 255);">&lt;/Directory&gt;</span></span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">3.<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(146, 144, 0);"> Set the permission to 644:</span></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">        =&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 47, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> sudo</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">chmo</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">d 644<span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);"> </span></span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/ec/apache2/users/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">khasanov.conf</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Loading Modules in the “httpd.conf”</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Edit the “/etc/apache2/httpd.conf” and make sure that the following module is loaded:</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 150, 255); font-family: Helvetica;">LoadModule</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica;"> </span><span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica;">userdir_module libexec/apache2/</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 150, 255); font-family: Helvetica;">mod_userdir.so</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica;"># Let to read what is in the “httpd-userdir.conf”:</span></div><div><font face="Courier" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Include</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> <span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/private/etc/apache2/extra/</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">httpd-userdir.conf</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><font color="#929292" face="Courier" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">#  Edit the "</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/etc/apache2/extra/httpd-userdir.conf”file add the following:</span></font></div><div><font color="#929292" face="Courier" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># ( if its not present )</span></font></div><div><font face="Courier" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Include</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> /private/etc/apache2/users/</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">*.conf</span></font></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 55, 255); font-family: Courier;">&lt;IfModule</span><span style="font-family: Courier;"> </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 150, 255); font-family: Courier;">bonjour_module</span><span style="font-family: Courier;">&gt;</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Courier;">       </span><span style="font-family: Courier; font-weight: bold;">RegisterUserSite</span><span style="font-family: Courier;"> customized-users</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 55, 255); font-family: Courier;">&lt;/IfModule&gt;</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 55, 255); font-family: Courier;"><br /></span></div><div><hr /></div><div><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Test the Configuration:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; <span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 47, 146); font-weight: normal;">sudo</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-weight: bold;"> apachectl </span></span><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(0, 144, 81);">restart</span></span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Visit <span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(121, 121, 121);">http:</span></span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(121, 121, 121); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">//localhost/~khasanov/</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">The Log Files:</span><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px;">=&gt; tail -f </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255);">/private/var/log/apache2/access_log</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px;">=&gt; tail -f</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255);"> /private/var/log/apache2/error_log</span></div><div><br /></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">How To see the Server Status</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div>In your /etc/apache2/httpd.conf uncomment these lines:</div><div>   <span style="font-weight: bold;"> </span><span style="font-weight: bold;">LoadModule</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 143, 0);"> status_module</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 150, 255);"> libexec/apache2/mod_status.so</span></div><div># Add this at the end of the file:</div><div>   <span style="font-weight: bold;"> Include</span> <span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/private/etc/apache2/extra/httpd-info.conf</span></div><div># Edit "Include <span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/private/etc/apache2/extra/httpd-info.conf</span>”</div><div># and modify the lines:</div><div>    <span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">&lt;Location</span> <span style="color: rgb(148, 55, 255);">/server-status&gt;</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 55, 255);">         SetHandler server-status </span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(148, 55, 255);">         Require host localhost </span></div><div>   <span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0);"> </span><span style="color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">&lt;/Location&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div>#  For “fullstatus” turn “on” :</div><div>    <span style="color: rgb(0, 143, 0);">ExtendedStatus On</span></div><div><br /></div><div><hr /></div><div><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">PHP Test</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># The PHP is installed by default and we have already loaded the PHP module in</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># the “http.conf” file. </span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># If you want to use the lastest version of PHP (i.e. php 7.1) see my notes .</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># Now we are going to write a PHP test file and put it under the “~/Sites” folder:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> vim</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;"> /Users/khasanov/Sites/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 143, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">testphp.php</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 55, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">&lt;?php</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">phpinfo();</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 55, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">?&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Visit “</span><span style="color: rgb(4, 51, 255);">http://localhost/~khasanov/php-info.php</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">” and you should see the PHP Info page.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><br /></span></div><div><hr /></div><div><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">MySQL Installation and Setup</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># MySQL is not the part of the OS X 10.11, so you need to download and install it.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># Get it from the MySQL site and use the Mac OS X 10.10 (x86, 64-bit), DMG Archive</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># version ( which works on 10.11).</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># Important ! You must write down a given temporary password which you need later.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># Passwd: </span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">NevuwZDG5w?e</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To start the MySQL Server:</span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">launchctl load -F</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Courier; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Courier; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/Library/LaunchDaemons/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">com.oracle.oss.mysql.mysqld.plist</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To stop the MySQL Server:</span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">launchctl unload -F </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Courier; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/Library/LaunchDaemons/</span></span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">com.oracle.oss.mysql.mysqld.plist</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To change the default ( temporary) password:</span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: italic; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/usr/local/mysql/bin/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mysqladmin</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> -u </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">root</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> -p'</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 64, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">temppassword</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">' </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">password</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> '</span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">newpassword</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">'</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To login as a root</span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: italic; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">/usr/local/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mysql</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> -v -u </span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 38, 0); font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">root</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> -p</span></font></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># To fix the 2002 MySQL Socket error:</span></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 47, 146);">sudo</span> </span><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mkdir</span></span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> <span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/var/mysql</span></span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> ln -s</span></span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> <span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/tmp/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 64, 255);">mysql.sock</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);"> /var/mysql/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 64, 255);">mysql.sock</span></span></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Courier; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 64, 255);"><br /></span></span></font></div><div><hr /></div><div><span style="font-size: 22px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">phpMyAdmin Installation and Configuration</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 16px;" color="#929292"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># Download the phpMyAdmin from </span><a href="https://www.phpmyadmin.net/" style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">https://www.phpmyadmin.net/</a></font></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># and extract it and then rename the folder to phpMyAdmin</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Step 1:  Copy the phpMyAdmin </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">root folder</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> to “</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">phpmyadmin"</span></font></div><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Step 2:  =&gt; </span></font><font style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal; color: rgb(255, 64, 255);">sudo</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal; font-weight: bold;"> cp -r</span> </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">phpmyadmin</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">  </span></font><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">/Library/WebServer/Documents/</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">( i.e.System document root ).</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Note: If you have installed the MySQL Server your way, you might still get </span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">Error: 2002 - No such file or </span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica;">directory</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span></div><hr /><div><font face="Helvetica" style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">How To Install and Configure the PHP 7.1 on MAC OS X</span></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica;"># Make sure that you have the “brew” installed. </span></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica;"># If not, please see my notes on “Installing Brew</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica;">”</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">brew install php@7.1</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"> </span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"># After the installation, you will get the following message and just follow what it says.</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"># Remember: <span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal;">The main configuration file is </span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;"> “</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(148, 17, 0); line-height: normal;">/etc/apache2</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">/</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(4, 51, 255); line-height: normal;">httpd.conf</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; line-height: normal;">”</span></span></div><div><hr /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"># To enable PHP in Apache add the following to httpd.conf and restart Apache:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">=&gt; <span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 47, 146);">sudo</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 47, 146); font-weight: bold;"> </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">vim</span> <span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">/etc/apache2/</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255);">httpd.conf</span></span></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;">    </span><span style="color: rgb(255, 47, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;">#LoadModule php5_module libexec/apache2/libphp5.so</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;">    </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 145, 147);">LoadModule</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"> </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255);">php7_module</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);"> /usr/local/opt/php@7.1/lib/httpd/modules/</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(4, 51, 255);">libphp7.so</span></div><div><font face="Helvetica" color="#929292"># Add the lines as shown below:</font></div><div>              <en-media hash="0bd9bbe1a72a95b4410fdb2d14adaa6a" type="image/png" style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(4, 51, 255);" /></div><div>         <br /></div><div> =&gt; <font color="#ff2f92">sudo<b> </b></font><b>apachectl </b><font color="#4f8f00">restart</font></div><div><font color="#929292"># Test by visiting to http://localhost/~khasanov/php-info.php</font></div><div><hr /></div><div><font color="#929292"># Setting Up the Time Zone</font></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"><font color="#929292"># The </font><font color="#9437ff">php.ini </font><font color="#929292">and </font><font color="#9437ff">php-fpm.ini</font><font color="#929292"> file can be found in</font><font color="#941100"> </font></span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"><font color="#941100"> /usr/local/etc/php/7.1/</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;">=&gt;</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 47, 146);"> sudo</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"> </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">vim</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"> </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 17, 0);">  /usr/local/etc/php/7.1/</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 55, 255);">php.ini</span></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(146, 146, 146); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"># Set the time zone:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">date.timezone</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px;"> = </span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(146, 144, 0);">America/Toronto</span></div><div><hr /></div><div><font face="Helvetica" size="4" color="#929292"># Making the PHP 7.1 as a default :</font></div><div><font face="Helvetica" size="4" color="#929292"># Edit the “~/.bash_profile” and add the lines as shown below:</font></div><div>    <en-media hash="7d897cf258c71287e6a424144bdb376d" type="image/png" style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;" /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;"># For compilers to find this software you may need to set:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">  <b>  LDFLAGS</b>:  -L/usr/local/opt/php@7.1/lib</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">  <b>  CPPFLAGS</b>: -I/usr/local/opt/php@7.1/include</span></div><div><br style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;" /></div><div><br style="font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px;" /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">To have launchd start php@7.1 now and restart at login:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">  brew services start php@7.1</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">Or, if you don't want/need a background service you can just run:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica;">  php-fpm</span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">  </span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div></en-note>